results.name: Product of exponents of prime factorization of n by prime signature: A005361(A025487).
link: Álvar Ibeas, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
program: (PARI) lista() = {v = readvec("b025487.txt"); for (i=1, #v, f = factor(v[i]); print1(prod(k=1, #f~, f[k,2]), ", "););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Nov 02 2014
